Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US farming in crisis
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xjfq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 17 Feb 1985
Farm bankruptcies rise as prices fall and Reagan sticks to planned cuts on subsidies. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less